📏 Agent Rules

 Mobile always sends images/PDFs as base64 strings to FastAPI
 All LLM calls use Gemini 2.0 Flash only — no other models
 Every agent must return structured JSON (BillJSON schema) — no free-form text except letter_gen
 Screens do one job — no multi-purpose screens
 Backend runs locally, tunneled via ngrok for hackathon demo


